query: SELECT ml.id, r.name as region_name, ml.status, ml.products_found, ml.new_restocks, ml.duration, ml.created_at FROM monitoring_logs ml JOIN regions r ON ml.region_id = r.id WHERE ml.created_at > '2026-01-02 09:17:00' ORDER BY ml.created_at DESC;
